                            <h5 class="card-title fw-bold text-center text-primary">Monitoring of Liquidation of the Scholarship Recipients</h5>
                            <h6 class="text-center text-warning mb-3"><i class="fas fa-university"></i> Sultan Kudarat State University</h6>
                            <p class="card-text text-center">The general objective of the study is to design, develop, and evaluate a centralized liquidation monitoring system that supports manual and ATM-based processes through a unified dashboard, flexible data entry, voucher recording, and digital attachment handling. The system aims to improve transparency by verifying and displaying liquidation proofs, streamline operations through automated approval and document routing to responsible officers, and support decision-making through structured reports on submissions, approvals, vouchers, and processing performance. The system will be assessed based on functionality, usability, acceptability, accuracy, and security to confirm that it meets operational and administrative needs.</p>
                            <div class="text-center mb-3">
                                <span class="badge bg-primary me-1 mb-1"><i class="fas fa-graduation-cap me-1"></i> Scholarship Management</span>
